OL,3,CMurder of 'loving' mother was
OL,4,C'burglary gone wrong', sister-in-law
OL,5,Ctells inquest
OL,7,FThe sister-in-law of a woman who was
OL,8,Fmurdered ten years ago in Leicester
OL,9,Fhas told an inquest she believes her
OL,10,Fdeath was a "burglary gone wrong".
OL,12,FMumtaz Member, 56, was found dead in
OL,13,Fher home in Holmfield Avenue,
OL,14,FStoneygate by her husband.
OL,16,FA postmortem examination revealed the
OL,17,Fmother-of-three had died from head
OL,18,Finjuries sometime between midnight and
OL,19,F9.30am on December 12th, 2015.
