OL,3,CMurder of 'loving' mother was
OL,4,C'burglary gone wrong', sister-in-law
OL,5,Ctells inquest
OL,7,FAt the inquest into her death, her
OL,8,Fsister-in-law, Munira Member, said she
OL,9,Fbelieves an intruder broke in.
OL,11,FAsked by the coroner when she thought
OL,12,Fit was a burglary, Ms Member said: "It
OL,13,Fwas when I realised the jewellry was
OL,14,Fmissing", adding that Mumtaz Member
OL,15,Fwore "gold bangles".
OL,17,FShe was then asked if she believed a
OL,18,Ffamily member had killed her sister-in-
OL,19,Flaw. Ms Member replied "no".
