OL,3,CMurder of 'loving' mother was
OL,4,C'burglary gone wrong', sister-in-law
OL,5,Ctells inquest
OL,7,FShe said if she had the "faintest idea
OL,8,Fwho was responsible" she would tell
OL,9,Fpolice.
OL,11,FMs Member told the inquest she was not
OL,12,Faware of any threats to the family,
OL,13,Fbut that she has increased security at
OL,14,Fher house since the incident in 2015.
OL,16,FSafwaan Member, Mumtaz's nephew, told
OL,17,Fthe inquest that Mumtaz was "like a
OL,18,Fmother to him".
