OL,5,Ctells inquest
OL,7,FSafwaan said he worked with Mohammed,
OL,8,FMumtaz's son, and said that he and his
OL,9,Fbrother Shafiq had a "lovely
OL,10,Frelationship with their mother".
OL,12,FHe said Fatima, Mumtaz's daughter-in-
OL,13,Flaw, also had a very good relationship
OL,14,Fwith Mrs Member - like a mother and
OL,15,Fdaughter.
