OL,3,CMurder of 'loving' mother was
OL,4,C'burglary gone wrong', sister-in-law
OL,5,Ctells inquest
OL,7,FAt the inquest, Safwaan was asked by
OL,8,Fthe lawyers representing the family if
OL,9,Fhe believes his cousins were
OL,10,Fresponsible for their mother's death.
OL,11,FHe said he did not think they were
OL,12,Fresponsible.
OL,14,FThe inquest continues.
